                        WHAT IS BOBBY APPROVAL?
                                   __________________________________________________________________

   Bobby is a well known software used for checking websites to esure
  they are accessible to people with disabilities. In our continuous
 search for reaching and serving all of our customers in the best way,
we are putting a great effort to serve our users with disabilities. In
order to achieve this in the best way, we are using multiple approaches
 to check our websites for accessibility. DIY website has gone through
rigorous human checks as well as other measures such as Bobby Approval
    and World Wide Web Consortium's (W3C) Web Content Accessibility
        Guidelines and proved to meet their highest standards.
    For more information on Bobby, please goto www.cast.org/bobby.
